Q  The answer must be a common activity that people do while knitting and listening to a radio. Knitting and watching television are not common activities together. Knitting and making blankets are the same thing, and not a common activity with a radio. Eating is not a common activity with knitting and a radio. Listening to music is the most common activity people do while knitting and using a radio. So the answer is listen to music (a). 

