Q  The answer must be a situation that is likely to happen when playing soccer and winning. Excitement is a common feeling when winning. Getting tired is also a common feeling after playing soccer. Overtime is a common situation in soccer when the game is tied and has to continue. Anger and fights are not common feelings when winning. So the answer is excitement (a).

