Q  The answer must be a place where people can do experiments with chemicals, including lighting alcohol on fire. A supermarket, bar, pub, and restaurants are all places where people can buy or drink alcohol, but not a place to do experiments with chemicals. A chemistry lab is the most relevant place to do such an experiment. So the answer is chemistry lab (e).

