Q  If yesterday was 12/31/1929, then yesterday is 12/31/1929. So the answer is 12/31/1929. There is no yesterday in the future of today, so there is no date in the future that is yesterday. So, the answer is 12/31/1929. 

Q:
Answer 12/31/1929 expected 12/31/1929
